    "philosophy": "Sir 自然对话表达质疑/不喜欢 → 系统检测 → 累积到对应 item (joke/protocol/concern/promise) → 自动降权或 archive. 不需 Sir 显式说'撤'.",
    "consumer": "jarvis_sir_skepticism.SkepticismDetector",
    "rules": [
      "(1) skepticism: Sir 真表达质疑/不喜欢/反对 — 算 1 次 skepticism_count",
      "(2) confusion: Sir 不理解但不是质疑 — 不算 (只 publish 不累积)",
      "(3) reactivation: Sir 重新提起 / 用某 phrase — skepticism_count 减 1 (Sir 反悔)"
    ],
    "decay_thresholds": {
      "count_1_weight": 0.7,
      "count_2_weight": 0.5,
      "count_3_action": "auto_archive"
    },
    "history_note": "Vocab 改动写 history. Sir 实测调",
    "extensible": "L7 reflector daemon 后期 LLM-propose 新 keyword 入 review_queue"
  },
